{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L193"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)rotatesToMatchCamera","role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" and the map is rotated, the annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view rotates. This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" the annotation has its rotation angle fixed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":". Set this property to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view’s rotation is important.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with the map.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/rotatesToMatchCamera":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with the map."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"}],"title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"title":"MLNAnnotationImage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIImage","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"}}}